# Chat Implementation

The application implements a simple chat interface that connects to AI APIs.

## Frontend Implementation

- [app/page.tsx](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/page.tsx) implements the chat UI with:
  - Message history state
  - Message input and submission
  - Loading state handling
  - Auto-scrolling to the latest message

## Backend Implementation

- [app/api/chat/route.ts](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/api/chat/route.ts) implements the API endpoint that:
  - Receives messages from the client
  - Forwards them to the Dashscope API (Alibaba Cloud's AI service)
  - Returns the AI response to the client
  - Handles errors appropriately

## Configuration

- [app/config.ts](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/config.ts) manages API keys for:
  - OpenAI API
  - Dashscope API
